<h1>RULES FOR THE GAME</h1>
<p>
<br><br><br><br>1)You have  4*4 grid which has numbers/alphabet hidden under the
tiles. The position of the numbers beneath the tiles randomly generated everytime the
page gets reloaded/visited.
<br><br>2)
On clicking the tile, it shows the number/alphabet hidden under the tile and the tile will be
be  opened until another random tile is being clicked.<br><br>3)
If the tiles do not match, then both tiles are hidden again.
When the two successive tiles on being clicked have the same alphabet/number beneath the
tiles, then the tiles should remain open, showing the matched number/alphabet, and should be
no longer clickable.<br><br>4) The aim of the game is to find out its twin number/alphabet from
the remining tiles on successive clicks.
<br><br>5)The game is complete when all tiles are open.<br><br><br><br><br><br>
